[ProMED-mail thanks Dr. Höfle-Hansen for sending in this information and the reference from which it came.

Evidence of Usutu virus infections in humans and wild birds has been emerging in various countries in Europe over the past several years. The article that Dr. Höfle-Hansen cites establishes Usutu virus-caused mortality in blackbirds in Italy as early as 1996, information that ProMED-mail has not posted previously. - Mod.TY

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4749481,75.]
